					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Orin, Chosen of Bhaal, has died by the DarkUrge's/party's hands.\r\n\r\nIf the DU deafted Orin, Bhaal will celebrate his new Chosen and force a decision on them - accept him, or he will reclaim his blood from them.\r\n\r\nIf the player was defeated, the player sees a linear scene where Bhaal inflicts his blood on them, leaving them with the urge to kill, but not his slayer powers."
				}
